name: JavaScript Data Structures
tagline: The Classics: Stacks, Queues, Trees, Graphs, Sets, Linked Lists...
body:
JSLinkedList, JSQueue, JSStack, JSSet so far. 

You can click one of the links above or below to view, download or fork the code. I've also extended a few of the built-in JS types for running and testing the data structures. 

This is a work in progress, not all structures are coded and/or committed yet.
